description:
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen within the Research and Development Department for a highly motivated and enthusiastic Business Manager&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder should be an excellent communicator, who will have responsibility for the design and implementation of the commercial strategy for research at Hampshire Hospitals, with specific focus on growth and revenue generation. This includes interpretation and implementation of strategy from national and governmental bodies including UK Research &amp; Innovation. The post holder will have lead responsibility for the development of a sustainable commercial research portfolio, working with other members of the R&amp;D Leadership Team&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Research and Development Business manager will proactively engage with all Trust departments and service providers to ensure that end-to-end commercial activity is achievable and realised, whilst supporting future collaboration and new opportunities in cohesive manner drawing on the clinical expertise in Hampshire Hospitals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a role that requires judgement, initiative and prioritisation as well as business and analytical skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post is based across all 3 sites, Basingstoke, Winchester and Andover. If you are interested in the post and would like to find out more please contact Natasha Chigbo, Head of Research and Development on 07920413184 or by email on natasha.chigbo@hhft.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Natasha Chigbo Head of Research and Development&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;natasha.chigbo@hhft.nhs.uk / 07920413184&lt;/p&gt;
